name: Shibgeki
description: Shibgeki is a community driven token that ressurected from inside the blockchain to save memecoins. $SHIBGEKI aims to become the 1st degen marketplace, connecting millions of degen devs, investors and partners around the space. In addition, $SHIBGEKI aims to deliver what a lot of projects have not yet quite succeeded which is the TitanLocker with small fees. $SHIBGEKI will also have a TitanDAO which should allow holders with GOV voting rights. $SHIBGEKI will be also donating 50% of all their tax income in the first 24 hours towards Ukraine.
